args: After all he did to make this village\nprosper... Who would do this?
It ain't just this village. Mayors, lords,\nand other big-timers are gettin' offed\nleft and right these days.
Hmm... Didn't we just hear about a pastor\nwho was killed as well? Could the same\nperson be responsible?
Whoever they are, they seem to be\ntargeting the virtuous. But why?
I dunno, boss, but it stinks to high heaven.\nI'll take a look around the area, see if I\ncan't dig up a few clues.
Somethin' about this don't feel right.\nI've got a major case'a the\nheebie-jeebies...
All right, who's there?!\nShow yer face, ya coward!
My identity is not important.\nFor I know exactly who you are...Ranzal.

Son of a lord. Heir to Saint Lotier.
A burly, weathered mercenary.
And now...a military commander
for New Alberia.
Privileged of birth. Privileged of body.\nPrivileged of friends.
Privilege is...an unforgivable sin.\nThose who bear it trample on those\nwho do not.
And that... That I cannot overlook.\nDo you hear me, Ranzal?\nDO YOU HEAR ME?!
I hear ya, but you're not makin'\nany damn sense!
I...am Volk. And I am sick.\nSick with WEAKNESS!
For what is weakness...but a disease?\nA rampant one.
It is spread like a plague by those\nborn under its heavy yoke.\nSurely even you can see that?
I'm tellin' ya, bub, you're not makin' a\nlick of sense!
You... You just happened to be privileged.
Happened to not catch the sickness.\nThat really is all there is to it.

But cheating sickness is a sin most vile—
for it is a product of privilege. And now,
Ranzal, you must repent. You...and
Zacharias both!
Hold on, what's my dad gotta do\nwith this?!
He will be made to suffer my disease.\nAs...will YOU!
Who are you? Are you the one responsible\nfor the recent string of murders?!
You're outta your gourd! The folks what\nyou've been killin' are the ones tryin'\nto SAVE the damn weak!
You were born to privilege.\nYou will never understand.
Do you think the weak yearn for strength?\nSuch is the depth of your privilege.

The weak wish only to SHARE their
weakness! They want everyone to
wallow with them in squalor and
irrelevance!
You think that justifies murder?!\nThat this is some crusade for\nthose less privileged?!
Heh. Heh heh...\nHa ha ha ha ha!\nHAAAAA HA HA HA HA HAAAAAAA!
Aha ha... Ha...\nWhat do you know of justice, prince?
What do you know of hardship?\nWhat COULD you know?!
Did he just create some sort of spacial\ndistortion?!
I am... WE are...fangs. For those without.\nWe are AGITO!
Now, feel my blade of purgation!
